ressure that B provides.\nGiven the weighting of reliability and calmness under pressure above other factors, **Candidate\u202fB** emerges as the most suitable choice for a long\u2011distance pilot despite his interpersonal flaws.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
