or response to criticism could jeopardize safety and crew harmony.\nGiven the weighting of reliability and calmness above other factors, **Candidate\u202fB** emerges as the most suitable choice for the long\u2011distance pilot position, despite his interpersonal shortcomings.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
